8#ifndef SRC_EDITION_ENTRY_PARSER_H_
9#define SRC_EDITION_ENTRY_PARSER_H_
10
11#include "src/chapter_atom_parser.h"
12#include "src/master_value_parser.h"
13#include "webm/dom_types.h"
14#include "webm/id.h"
15
16namespace webm {
17
18// Spec reference:
19// http://matroska.org/technical/specs/index.html#EditionEntry
20// http://www.webmproject.org/docs/container/#EditionEntry
21class EditionEntryParser : public MasterValueParser<EditionEntry> {
22 public:
23 EditionEntryParser()
24 : MasterValueParser<EditionEntry>(MakeChild<ChapterAtomParser>(
25 Id::kChapterAtom, &EditionEntry::atoms)) {}
26
27 protected:
28 Status OnParseCompleted(Callback* callback) override {
29 return callback->OnEditionEntry(metadata(Id::kEditionEntry), value());
30 }
31};
32
33} // namespace webm
34
35#endif // SRC_EDITION_ENTRY_PARSER_H_
